public class MarkupFeatureElement
extends BaseFeatureElement

Maintains the "state" information for a BaseFeatureElement on an acetate layer. The current states supported are, 

     UserAdded:  Any feature added by the user
     Modified:   A modified feature from the markup layer
     Clean:      An exact same (unmodified) feature from the markup layer
